<twig:LayoutBox>
	<header class="flex items-start justify-between">
		<div>
			<twig:H2>Investissements</twig:H2>
			<twig:H5>Investissements par planète</twig:H5>
		</div>

		<twig:Tooltip>
			Dans la rubrique « Investissements » sont répertoriés tous les investissements relatifs à l’école
			de commandement et au contre-espionnage. Chacun de ces investissements peuvent être gérés dans leur bâtiment respectif. Faites attention
			à ne pas avoir plus d’investissements que de recettes.
		</twig:Tooltip>
	</header>

	<section class="mt-4">
		<ul class="flex flex-col divide-y divide-gray-500 border-y border-gray-500">
			{% for planet in player_planets %}
				{% set base_invest = planet.iSchool + planet.iAntiSpy %}

				<li class="">
					<details class="marker:content-['']" name="base-investments">
						<summary class="cursor-pointer flex items-center justify-between py-2">
							<span>
								<span class="px-2 text-light{{ current_player.faction.identifier }}">↓</span>
								<span style="font-variant: all-small-caps" class="label">{{ planet.name }}</span><br>
							</span>

							<span class="text-sm">{{- base_invest|number -}}</span>
						</summary>

						<div>
							<ul class="sub-list-type-1" id="invest-base-{{ planet.id }}">
								<li>
									<label for="school-form-base-{{ planet.id }}" class="flex justify-between items-center">
										<span>école de cmd.</span>
										<span class="value">
											{{- planet.iSchool|number -}}
										</span>
									</label>

									<form action="{{ path('update_planet_investments', {'planetId': planet.id, 'category': 'school'}) }}" method="POST" id="school-form-base-{{ planet.id }}" class="flex py-2">
										<twig:Input type="text" name="credit" value="{{ planet.iSchool }}" class="w-48" />
										<twig:Button type="submit" :faction="current_player.faction">
											ok
										</twig:Button>
									</form>
								</li>
								<li>
									<label for="spying-form-base-{{ planet.id }}" class="flex items-center justify-between">
										<span class="label">contre-espionnage</span>
										<span class="value">
											{{- planet.iAntiSpy|number -}}
										</span>
									</label>

									<form action="{{ path('update_planet_investments', {'planetId': planet.id, 'category': 'antispy'}) }}" method="POST" id="spying-form-base-{{ planet.id }}" class="flex py-2">
										<twig:Input type="text" name="credit" value="{{ planet.iAntiSpy }}" class="w-48" />
										<twig:Button type="submit" :faction="current_player.faction">
											ok
										</twig:Button>
									</form>
								</li>
							</ul>
						</div>
					</details>
				</li>
			{% endfor %}

			<li class="flex justify-between items-center py-2">
				<strong>total des investissements</strong>
				<span>
					{{- investments_data.totalInvest|number -}}
				</span>
			</li>
		</ul>
	</section>
</twig:LayoutBox>
